{"tid":2320960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人　只是公德心比個人自由大","createTime":"2020-12-11T07:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T08:39:12.000Z","uid":261647,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"daa1b856d1b9e8076a446e3566124f0bd1e30534","tid":2320960,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T07:50:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Currenteventsdigest/posts/2576609912630132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCurrenteventsdigest%2Fposts%2F2576609912630132&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=d3fd0836\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Currenteventsdigest/posts/2576609912630132</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：盧斯達<br />\n<br />\n一般人趕著六點之前喝完最後一口堂食咖啡，港島那邊的富婆可能還剛醒不久，宿醉未醒，不知今日如何打發；一般人在輿論上日日受到政府和甩皮甩骨網民的鞭韃。有確診數字，有人說是因為鳩戴口罩、專家說是因為一般人外出購物、低級一點的則說是因為香港人全民驗毒率不足。香港人都是善男信女，默默承受攻擊和指責，但還是會默默抗疫，這不是奴性，而是港英以來培育的公德心。究竟香港人為何會有公德心，我是不明白的，但他們就是有，於是他們也會管理好自己，充滿自治質素；世衛還在說病毒沒有傳染性、不用旅行禁令，他們就自己行動。港人未曾政治自治，但對國際、地區大台的幻想逐一崩潰，香港人個人層面的自治越發強橫，因為不信而得救，沒有其他地方比得上。"},{"pid":"38e2447b0a9a3efa7870f2183def61674a641a93","tid":2320960,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"香港人有公德心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d97fc31106bfc0d94f3e29f7df9912d01a2c8a95","tid":2320960,"uid":276508,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"38e2447b0a9a3efa7870f2183def61674a641a93","tid":2320960,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"香港人有公德心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:21:57.000Z","msg":"上年疫情啱啱開始個陣<br />\n幾多手足去派口罩<br />\n你依d淨係識踩抵香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a316ffb352284866d213a536d6b357e7a19f304","tid":2320960,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"38e2447b0a9a3efa7870f2183def61674a641a93","tid":2320960,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"香港人有公德心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T08:39:12.000Z","msg":"笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n驚自己死驚傳染人啦屌港豬"}]}